 challenger app for social anxiety disorder: new advances in mobile psychological treatment. Internet Interv. <strong class=\"EmphasisTypeBold \">2</strong>(4), 382\u2013391 (2015)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=The%20challenger%20app%20for%20social%20anxiety%20disorder%3A%20new%20advances%20in%20mobile%20psychological%20treatment&amp;author=A.%20Miloff&amp;author=A.%20Marklund&amp;author=P.%20Carlbring&amp;journal=Internet%20Interv.&amp;volume=2&amp;issue=4&amp;pages=382-391&amp;publication_year=2015\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">29.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR29\">Uniwhere. <span class=\"ExternalRef\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www.uniwhere.com/\"><span class=\"RefSource\">https://www.uniwhere.com/</span></a></span>. Accessed 24 Feb 2020<span class=\"Occurrences\"></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">30.</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR30\">Kosow, H., Ga\u00dfner, R.: Methods of future and scenario analysis: overview, assessment, and selection criteria. DEU, Bonn (2008)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Methods%20of%20future%20and%20scenario%20analysis%3A%20overview%2C%20assessment%2C%20and%20selection%20criteria&amp;author=H.%20Kosow&amp;author=R.%20Ga%C3%9Fner&amp;publication_year=2008\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li></ol></div></section><section class=\"Section1 RenderAsSection1\"><h2 class=\"Heading\" id=\"copyrightInformation\">Copy